{
  "stem": "7777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told you what this was and-- ay, you see these little thin Poles with the wires?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They will stay four, six weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they will-- and he bring-- always, everyday he got news the German is getting [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK, what can you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I know it's not possible to exist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was all around kill the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They [NON-ENGLISH] told this Judenrate in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Ludma, ?] you are good people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You will live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to your town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- I was not believing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Only, he said so, he said so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We work over there till-- till [INAUDIBLE], 17 days in [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Hillel. ?] And later, they make the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They make the ghetto in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Ludma. ?] And people was going to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If-- if a policeman saw you in the street and he was thinking maybe you carrying home something, he shot you right in the place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because usually, you go out, you take a shirt, you take a jacket, you give it to a Gentile, he'll give you a chicken, or give you some bread, give you some butter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And if a policeman was thinking you carry something and he find you, he shot you right in the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And nobody can do something there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- this was going like this, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember 17 days in [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE], before Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now the [INAUDIBLE] when we worked in the mill is the [NON-ENGLISH] give an order, he come to the Judenrate-- the blueprint-- and he said, over there, six kilometer from [?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ludma, ?] is big woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we have to bring tanks here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to make-- dig holes to come hide the tanks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he give out a plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
